sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant Node as Node/TypeScript Gateway
    participant Python as Python Worker

    Browser->>Node: audio_input\n{type: "audio_input", audioBase64: "..."}
    Node->>Python: process_audio\n{type: "process_audio", requestId: "abc123", audioBase64: "..."}
    Python->>Node: audio_result\n{type: "audio_result", requestId: "abc123", transcript: "...", assistantText: "...", audioBase64: "..."}
    Node->>Browser: audio_result\nSame payload returned to client
